# Allow Firebase Google Sign-In popups to communicate their result back to this page.
# Without this, some browsers sever the popup's window.opener and the popup just closes
# with no login (the "popup opens then immediately closes" symptom). The app also falls
# back to signInWithRedirect, but this lets the faster popup flow work directly.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin-allow-popups
